item.title: CVE-2024-35297|2024-05-27T04:40:54.654Z -- aviplugins.com -- WP Booking
item.description: Cross-site scripting vulnerability exists in WP Booking versions prior to 2.4.5. If this vulnerability is exploited, an arbitrary script may be executed on the web browser of the user who is accessing the web site using the product.
